<section class="suds-policy page-width">
  <div class="suds-policy__wrap">
    <p class="suds-policy__eyebrow">Suds Auto Salon policy</p>
    <h1>Refund Policy</h1>

    <div class="rte">
      <h2>Mobile detailing appointments</h2>
      <p>Suds Auto Salon is an appointment-based mobile detailing service. If something reasonable was missed during your detail, contact sudsautosalon@gmail.com as soon as possible so Sam can review it and, when appropriate, correct it.</p>

      <h2>Deposits and rescheduling</h2>
      <p>Deposits may be required to reserve appointment time. Rescheduling depends on notice, weather, route timing, and availability. No-shows or last-minute cancellations may affect deposit eligibility.</p>

      <h2>Physical products</h2>
      <p>If a physical product is sold through the store, contact sudsautosalon@gmail.com to receive return instructions and the current shipping address before sending anything back.</p>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>For refund, return, or appointment concerns, email sudsautosalon@gmail.com or text (425) 361-8838 with your name, appointment date, vehicle, and issue.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .suds-policy {
    padding-top: clamp(48px, 7vw, 86px);
    padding-bottom: clamp(56px, 8vw, 100px);
  }

  .suds-policy__wrap {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .suds-policy__eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #8c6b05;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: .06em;
    line-height: 1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .suds-policy h1 {
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    color: #101010;
    font-size: clamp(3.8rem, 6vw, 6.4rem);
    line-height: .96;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Suds refund policy",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
